[
    {
        "text": "You probably know your blood type -- A?",
        "start": 1.229,
        "duration": 2.731
    },
    {
        "text": "B?",
        "start": 3.96,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Universal donor?",
        "start": 5.08,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "You might even carry a card on you",
        "start": 6.64,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "so that in case of emergency,",
        "start": 8.46,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "you won’t get the wrong type of blood.",
        "start": 10.24,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "But do you know how your blood type",
        "start": 12.12,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "was actually identified in the first place?",
        "start": 13.74,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Blood type can be determined in two ways:",
        "start": 16.46,
        "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
        "text": "forward blood grouping which detects markers",
        "start": 18.6,
        "duration": 2.66
    },
    {
        "text": "on the blood cells themselves,",
        "start": 21.28,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "And reverse blood grouping,",
        "start": 23.26,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "which detects antibodies present",
        "start": 24.74,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "in the blood plasma",
        "start": 26.58,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Either type of test today takes a long time,",
        "start": 28.82,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "requires technical training, and can be expensive",
        "start": 31.2,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Researchers have been working",
        "start": 34.98,
        "duration": 1.1
    },
    {
        "text": "on a new blood typing test",
        "start": 36.08,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "that is not only easy to use,",
        "start": 37.6,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "but can be done on site --",
        "start": 39.1,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "in as little as 30 seconds",
        "start": 40.74,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "A small blood sample is dropped",
        "start": 43.94,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "into the middle of the testing strip",
        "start": 45.32,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "A color change in either observation window",
        "start": 47.64,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "delivers the results",
        "start": 49.5,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "This test can perform forward",
        "start": 51.5,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "and reverse blood grouping",
        "start": 52.76,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "at the same time which gives",
        "start": 53.76,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "more confidence in the result",
        "start": 55.3,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "A similar test can also be used",
        "start": 57.62,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "to determine rare blood types",
        "start": 59.14,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "After the blood is loaded onto the disc,  the blood",
        "start": 61.16,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "spectroscopy is used to automatically",
        "start": 63.2,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "determine the blood type,",
        "start": 65.5,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "So a person doesn’t need",
        "start": 67.16,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "to interpret the color change",
        "start": 68.18,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "and the test can be done by someone",
        "start": 69.74,
        "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
        "text": "who is colorblind",
        "start": 70.92,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Until now paper-based tests were reliant",
        "start": 72.08,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "on blood samples that had already been spun in",
        "start": 74.02,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "a centrifuge, which takes time and experience.",
        "start": 76.12,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "The introduction of these test strips",
        "start": 79.8,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "has the potential to not only",
        "start": 81.56,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "save time and money in the hospital",
        "start": 82.64,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "but in remote areas with few resources,",
        "start": 84.6,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "rapid blood typing could be done by non-trained",
        "start": 86.8,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "users and blood supplies can be stretched",
        "start": 89.0,
        "duration": 2.42
    }
]